sequenceDiagram
  actor S as Sender
  participant FE as Frontend Chat
  participant WS as Socket.IO Server
  participant DB as MongoDB Message
  participant R as Receiver Frontend

  S->>FE: Type and send message
  FE->>WS: emit message:send(payload)
  WS->>WS: Ensure member + canPost + rate limit
  WS->>WS: Sanitize content
  WS->>DB: Create Message
  DB-->>WS: Message saved
  WS-->>FE: ACK ok
  WS-->>R: emit message:new to room
  R->>R: Render incoming message
  R->>WS: emit message:delivered / message:read
  WS-->>FE: delivery/read status events
